OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FSome breaks
OL,6,Fin the cloud possible giving a
OL,7,Fbrighter end to the day, perhaps an
OL,8,Fisolated light shower. Skies turning
OL,9,Fcloudy again towards dawn. Blustery
OL,10,Fwinds gradually easing through the
OL,11,Fevening, remaining lighter overnight.
OL,12,
OL,13,CSaturday:FCloud and light patchy rain
OL,14,Fquickly spreading northwards, some
OL,15,Fbrighter spells possible from
OL,16,Fafternoon onwards. Turning
OL,17,Fincreasingly windy as Storm Dave
OL,18,Farrives with gales developing from mid-
OL,19,Fafternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
