OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FBright
OL,6,Fbut blustery on Easter Sunday, with
OL,7,Fscattered showers. Winds easing
OL,8,Fleaving a drier, brighter, and warmer
OL,9,FEaster Monday. Generally settled on
OL,10,FTuesday, potential for cloud and
OL,11,Fisolated showers later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
